│   // To keep things simple, only process loops with single latch. We                                                                                                                                    │
│   // canonicalize most loops to this form. We can support multi-latch if needed.                                                                                                                        │
│   if (!L.getLoopLatch())                                                                                                                                                                                │
│     return false;                                                                                                                                                                                       │
